{{vgname|漫威英雄 Online|en=Marvel Heroes Online}}是一款以[[漫威漫畫|漫威漫畫]]世界為背景的[[大型多人線上角色扮演遊戲|大型多人線上角色扮演遊戲]]。,<ref name="Heroes">{{cite web|url=http://news.mmosite.com/content/a/2011-12-20/marvel_superhero_mmo_officially_dubbed_marvel_heroes.shtml|title=Marvel Universe MMO Officially Dubbed Marvel Heroes|accessdate=2012-01-13|date=2011-12-20|work=MMO Site|author=Will|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120107214046/http://news.mmosite.com/content/a/2011-12-20/marvel_superhero_mmo_officially_dubbed_marvel_heroes.shtml|archive-date=2012-01-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>玩家在遊戲中扮演漫威世界的[[超級英雄|超級英雄]]，對付[[九頭蛇_(漫威漫畫)|九頭蛇]]等反派以拯救世界。遊戲並提供英文、法文、繁體中文等多種語言以供不同語言和國家的使用者遊玩。

2017年11月15日，迪士尼宣布關閉本遊戲<ref name="auto">{{Cite news|url=https://kotaku.com/disney-shuts-down-marvel-heroes-1820475273|title=Disney Shuts Down Marvel Heroes|last=D'Anastasio|first=Cecilia|work=Kotaku|access-date=2017-11-15|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302071208/https://kotaku.com/disney-shuts-down-marvel-heroes-1820475273|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於同月27日結束營運<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/11/23/marvel-heroes-developer-gazillion-reportedly-shut-down-game-to-close-early|title=Marvel Heroes Developer Gazillion Reportedly Shut Down, Game to Close Early|first=Lucy|last=O'Brien|date=22 November 2017|publisher=|access-date=2018-05-14|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226150152/https://www.ign.com/articles/2017/11/23/marvel-heroes-developer-gazillion-reportedly-shut-down-game-to-close-early|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vg247.com/2017/11/23/multiple-sources-are-claiming-that-marvel-heroes-will-shut-down-a-month-early-with-gazillion-laying-off-all-employees/|title=Marvel Heroes Omega is offline on all platforms - VG247|date=28 November 2017|publisher=|access-date=2018-05-14|archive-date=2017-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171123022505/https://www.vg247.com/2017/11/23/multiple-sources-are-claiming-that-marvel-heroes-will-shut-down-a-month-early-with-gazillion-laying-off-all-employees/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2017/11/22/gazillion-terminated-staff-shutting-marvel-heroes-friday/ Gazillion Has Terminated its Staff and Shutting Down Marvel Heroes on Friday] {{Wayback|url=http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2017/11/22/gazillion-terminated-staff-shutting-marvel-heroes-friday/ |date=20180913203210 }} - PlayStation LifeStyle</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/marvelheroes/status/935252377942179840|title=pic.twitter.com/Q12AUQ61c3|first=Marvel Heroes|last=Omega|date=27 November 2017|publisher=|access